name: Sandman
description: The frightening phenomena plaguing the galaxy continue to escalate and the cracks in reality itself have begun to show. But are these traces of the mind of an erratic deity - or a very real assault on the universe itself?
rules:
-- Unique Dominion, Ferengi Traditionalist, and Section 31 Faction Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using Valeo Beta V La'an, any version of Gant, T. Mayweather, Leland, or Desperate crew will provide a bonus to Event Faction Missions.
-- Every Event Faction Mission you succeed at earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Victory Points to unlock Event Threshold Rewards.
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Valeo Beta V La'an, Gant, T. Mayweather, Leland, or Desperate
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Missions!

featured_crew.name: Trip
featured_crew.flavor: Tucker was faced with the fact that if you play a ‘game’ on an alien ship, you can not only have fun, but also get pregnant.

featured_crew.name: Mayweather
featured_crew.flavor: Travis was found tied to a repair station. It seems he is dead, but there is still a chance to save him.

featured_crew.name: Spock
featured_crew.flavor: With the help of the Talosians, Spock shows Burnham how and why he escaped from the hospital and that he did not kill anyone.
